text: Jaroslav Kollinger (13 December 1905 - 24 July 1949) was a Czech gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:1949 deaths Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Roudnice nad Labem
